author: VR Gorilla - Virtual Reality & 360 Videos
description:
Download TriptoVR in the Meta-store now and start exploring!

Find the app on the *Meta Quest* store here.

https://www.meta.com/experiences/6447684138675693/

You dream of seeing the world? but life gets in the way?
You don’t have the time, the budget, or simply are unable to travel?
With TriptoVR, the world is within reach.
Step into stunning destinations, like Bali, Tokyo, Venice, New York all filmed for virtual reality – no flights, no barriers.. 
Instantly feel inspired and relaxed, like you are on holiday
Just put on your Meta Quest  and start exploring
TriptoVR – The world at your fingertips.
title: TriptoVR: The world is at your fingertips.
